---
import foundersStory from "../assets/founders-story-v2.png";
---

<section class="bg-[#FAFAF8] py-20">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-[#5D9C59] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sm font-semibold">
          Our Journey
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-5 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#2F3A45] leading-tight">
          A foundation built around children first.
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-8 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Children First Foundation was created after seeing how many children were held back not by talent, but by limited access to learning support, encouragement and opportunity.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          The founders began with a simple commitment: work alongside families, volunteers and communities to make education feel reachable, personal and full of possibility.
        </p>
      </div>

      <img
        src={foundersStory.src}
        alt="Founders Story"
        class="w-full rounded-3xl aspect-[4/5] object-cover"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
